Package ru.rusetskii.cashmachine.command

package ru.rusetskii.cashmachine.command
Command operations
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    Command
    Command is the abstract base class for all commands which allows application to execute different business logic A Command object encapsulates the state information needed for the various command operations.
    CommandFactory
    Stores all available commands and produces commands based on their arguments
    Processor
    Takes input parameters, creates command and executes it
